# ⚡ Cache Usage Example API

Demonstrates how Redis cache is used in FastAPI routes.

---

## 🧱 API Implementation

```python
from fastapi import APIRouter
from app.core.cache import get_cache, set_cache

router = APIRouter()

@router.get("/cached-data")
def cached_data():

    cached = get_cache("demo_key")

    if cached:
        return {"source": "cache", "data": cached}

    data = {"message": "fresh database response"}

    set_cache("demo_key", str(data), ttl=60)

    return {"source": "db", "data": data}
